Package: simplefreqs
Type: Package
Title: Simple Frequency Tables 
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person("Martin", "Barron", email = "martin@barron.cc",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Produces easy to read frequency tables. Function works both on the console 
    and in Rmarkdown and Quarto documents. It provides sensible default values and
    ability to easily produce accompanying graph, sort results, and weight frequencies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 1.1), 
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4), 
    rlang (>= 1.1), 
    gt(>= 0.9)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    knitr (>= 1.43),
    rmarkdown (>= 2.23),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
